title: 3 Bedroom Townhouse in Golden Acres Estate
description:
SOLE MANDATE 

Modern Townhouse in Golden Acres Estate 

UNIT DESCRIPTION
-3 bedrooms with lots of cupboards
- 2 bathrooms fully Tiled 
- spacious open plan kitchen with 5 plate gas stove and open plan living area
- the kitchen is fitted with Caesar stone counter tops  
- Double Garage with laundry area 

Golden Acres is a private, water-front estate, with beautiful views across the Tzaneen dam and towards the majestic mountains of Magoebaskloof and Georges Valley. It is situated in the up market suburb of Aquapark in Tzaneen, and is nestled between the Tzaneen dam and the rest of Aquapark. The estate is completely enclosed and offers 24 hour secured access, with guards situated at the controlled access gates, as well as on patrol. The Estate offers a range of opportunities to the most discerning investor, as well as to home owners wanting to develop their dream house.
The estate has more than a kilometer of dam front and owners have direct access to the water from the estate.

The development also boasts its own clubhouse that includes a gym, swimming pool, squash court and entertainment area. Furthermore, there are a number of open park areas within the estate which gives one the feel of wide open spaces. The squash courts and gym can be used by paying a small fee. The clubhouse and swimming pool can be used but T&C's apply.

title: Old Castle Brewery, Woodstock Office And  Residential
description:
The Old Castle Brewery is located on Beach Road Woodstock and is full of rich heritage and character.   Each office has a rustic feel,  with  modern glass and steel furnishings.  Originally constructed by  New York architect and Engineer, H Steinmann. The construction period was from 1900 to 1902,  It has been recently converted to A grade office and residential suites. 

Situated in the trendy area of Woodstock, just off the N1 and in close proximity to the N2.  The Old Castle Building is also 5 minutes drive from the CBD.  Close to all amenities and public transport routes.

The office park consists of a number of buildings with a mix of tenants and has great amenities such as a café and coffee shop, secured covered parking and 24 for hour security and access control.

This office has 3 levels
the ground floor is 73m2
1st floor is 63m2
2nd floor is 61m2

All units can be used for work and residential purposes
24 hr access and security
Fibre Ready
Bathroom with Shower

Please contact the agent for an exclusive viewing

title: House for sale in van riebeeckstrand, melkbosstrand
description:
Welcome to your new home… a spacious and large architectural marvel with stunning sea views. 

This spectacular home is a mixture of contemporary and industrial flair - a seaside abode for the large family where one can experience the very best that Melkbos has to offer.

Offering accommodation over three expansive levels - 5 bedrooms, each with their own en-suite bathroom as well as a large kitchen, dining and living area. Large covered balconies connects the indoors with the outdoors through the sliding doors from the open living areas. 

Stacker doors open up to another large outdoor space with sea views, perfect for outdoor dining and entertaining. The home offers a large decked outdoor space with a stunning pool and firepit area. There is also an extra large studio space, which can be converted into a separate flat. 

Come experience this one of a kind property for yourself and arrange a viewing with me today.

title: Apartment / flat for sale in table view, blouberg
description:
This fully furnished 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment in gorgeous Blaauwberg beckons you. Wake up refreshed in this well lit space where the views go beyond the horizon. A private balcony provides the perfect spot for a sundowner. 

It offers the following amenities, a coin operated laundry mat, a rooftop gym, as well as rooftop pool, front desk, 24 hour security as well as covered parking within the building. The apartment is a shot walk from public transportation and is well stocked with restaurants as well as other amenities all with a 5 minute walk.

The apartment can be managed on your behalf, so you can earn while sleeping. Do not let this amazing property pass you by.

title: Apartment / flat for sale in table view, blouberg
description:
These modern 2-3 bedroom apartments come fully furnished and boast high quality finishes, drop down ceilings and large windows that provide ample natural lighting. The open plan kitchen offers exquisite granite tops, plenty of cupboard space, a fridge, microwave and space for a dishwasher.  

The spacious living area is drenched in natural light and offers a mesh of comfort and entertainment that leads to a balcony, which offers a breath of fresh air.

Each one of the spacious bedrooms is fitted with ceiling fans, built in cupboards and large windows that allow for ample natural light. All apartments have balconies that offer enchanting views, of either Table Mountain, the Atlantic Ocean or Blouberg surrounding areas. 

Amenities include: a gymnasium; rooftop pool with a lounging area; De’Vara Spa can be found on the 11th floor; a dental laboratory; a 5 level secure parking; DSTV; internet; intercom systems as well as 24 hour on-site security.

The apartments are booked out 70% of the year and will offer great returns for any investor.

16 more units available ranging from R 3 100 000 to R 3 900 000 .
